{"tid":2246013,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"WWF董事會與商界關係密切 聘退休警官任CEO","createTime":"2020-10-16T16:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T08:24:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"98f9feb6540ff9282ba0852f4f23b4315bb88e68","tid":2246013,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ibDbeXdtQIIrOfgUBBPc56zfYGI=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O5UJO547BRGRTH2CCJHTLETVNM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FibDbeXdtQIIrOfgUBBPc56zfYGI%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO5UJO547BRGRTH2CCJHTLETVNM.png&h=667d1278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">前助理警務處長江偉智（Peter Cornthwaite）在2016年6月加入WWF擔任行政總裁（左）；前西九龍交通總督察盧永賢（Guy Lown）2017年加入WWF擔任業務經理（右）。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nWWF是本港最大規模、收入最高的環團之一，去年財政收入逾1.2億元，當中個人捐款就佔7,000萬元。而漁護署每年都資助WWF管理米埔，2019至20年度就資助356萬元。近年有前警官加入WWF任職高層，例如前助理警務處長江偉智（Peter Cornthwaite）在2016年6月加入WWF擔任行政總裁，而前西九龍交通總督察盧永賢（Guy Lown）退休後亦加入WWF擔任業務經理。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">WWF一直被視為與商界合作最緊密的環保組織，董事會主席是廣東省政協香港委員何聞達，董事吳宗權是會德豐主席。WWF理事亦有很多地產商，例如信和集團副主席吳永光、其士國際集團非執行董事周維正、恒隆集團主席陳啟宗等。WWF曾與長實合作發展鄰近米埔濕地的元朗豐樂圍住宅項目，其後豐樂圍發現米埔屈翅螢，在爭議聲中WWF最終擱置參與豐樂圍項目。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201017/OJX4F23KOBGKPG3IXT27HIISVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201017%2FOJX4F23KOBGKPG3IXT27HIISVE%2F&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=2eaf1588\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201017%2FOJX4F23KOBGKPG3IXT27HIISVE%2F&h=ed41abcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201017/OJX4F23KOBGKPG3IXT27HIISVE/</a>"},{"pid":"0f74fffb9bff8ec092b